            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報24722點，跌24點，較上日現貨收市價24773點低水51點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5451點，跌2點，低水2點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報8864點，跌21點，低水19點。</p>\n</div>",
